2002-05-16  Gonzalo Paniagua Javier <gonzalo@ximian.com>

	* aspelements.cs:
	(ServerObjectTag): new class for <object ...>.
	(Component): determine whether the component allows children or not.
	
	* generator.cs: use the new AllowChildren property for server controls.
	Added new function to process ServerObjectTag.

2002-05-14  Gonzalo Paniagua Javier <gonzalo@ximian.com>

	* aspelements.cs: assign a default name to controls without ID
	attribute.

	* generator.cs: fixed Style properties setting. 

	* Makefile: changed the name of the executable.

	* driver.cs: pass the file name without dirs to Generator.

2002-05-14  Gonzalo Paniagua Javier <gonzalo@ximian.com>

	* asp-tokenizer: allow '-' to be in an identifier (Font-Size).

	* aspelements.cs: modified TagAttributes to allow duplicate attribute
	names for plain HTML tags.

	* generator.cs: support for more property types in attributes (Styles,
	integers, bool, Unit, FontUnit). Support for GenericControl.

